cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper analyzes the topology and content of the darknet, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of machine learning for content categorization also falls under the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The study of the darknet and its illegal activities can also be classified under cybercrime (cs.CY) and systems and control (cs.SD).
